        Extends HDOT with the given new class and embeds it under the given parent.
        Parameters:
        newClass - the class to be integrated in the ontology
        parent - the parent class of the new class
        definitions - the definitions of the new class
        isTheActualHit - true if the new class is the hit and false if the new class is one of the subclasses of the hit
